title: Hi-Fi.Choice.-.April.2018
description: Inside the April issue we take an exclusive In-depth look at Focal’s Kanta No2 fashionable floorstander, while Exotica features Simaudio’s £7,300 Moon Evolution 600i v2 integrated amplifier and our regular reviews section features Mytek’s Liberty DAC, Neat Acoustics’ Iota Xplorer floorstanding loudspeaker, Audio-Technica’s flagship over-ear headphone as well as NAD’s D 3020 V2 amplifier/DAC. Plus, Music Legends salutes Ry Cooder and our Group Test looks at six interconnect and speaker cable combos from Atlas, Black Rhodium, Chord Company, Ecosse Cables, KLE Innovations and QED
